<br>
I just recently dinged my Iksar Monk to level 40. Now, I would like to update my hand to hand weapon. I am using a Polished Steel Ulak in my secondary because I am using a Guard Captain's Mallot in primary. I have about 1800pp to maybe 3kpp to spend if necessary. Any suggestions? <br>
<br>
Also, are their any range slot items that can be used for stat purpose that can be equiped while I have my primary and secondary filled? I was told that some items can not go in range slot when you have both primary and secondary occupied?<br>
<br>
Thank you<br>
<br>
Thorrax  <p><center>
<img src="http://members.aol.com/italrishguy/thorjuly.jpg">
</center> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unamsundeathmonkey.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Namsun DeathMonkey</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 858<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/1/02 4:05:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11682.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hand to Hand weapon help</span><hr size=1> Goranga Idol is great in the range slot for stat boosts, it doesn't cost too much these days because it's so common.  I have no idea what items can't go in range when primary and secondary are equipped...but the Goranga Idol can and you can't really get much better for quite a while hehe.<br>
<br>
As far as good H2H weapons go I'm a little out of the loop...but if Knuckle Dusters have become H2H weapons then that's a solid weapon you could use that would cost 1k. <p><center><IMG SRC=http://namsun.homestead.com/files/eqpics/namsunsig2.jpg><br>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=161080>Celestial Monkey</a> of the 59th Order <br>
Member of <A HREF=http://www.tkagiro.com>T`kagi Ro</A>, Fennin Ro</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uugle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ugle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 91<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/1/02 4:21:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11682.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://ugleduklin.tripod.com/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderpictures/dscn0011s.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hand to Hand weapon help</span><hr size=1> Fist of rock is 7/18 H2H.  Usually sells on Inny for 1600-2K.  Fist of Iron and better are nice but are going to be way more then 3K.  <br>
<br>
I've never seen Patriarch Claws sold (11/23), but since they drop in Scarlet Desert they might fit your price range (I have no idea on pricing), ditto on Putrid Claws (14/30).  For cheap go with a Master Eichatka (7/20).  They drop from a Grimling Foreman in Tenebrous and are fairly common.  Since a lot of people kill them for Acrylia Ore I wouldn't expect to pay more then a 1-200PP.  There's also the Wooden Hilted Ulak at 8/20 with a proc which is nice, drops from a &quot;boss&quot; MOB in DSP, though he's only around L51 heh. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ushiaa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shiaa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/1/02 4:58:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11682.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hand to Hand weapon help</span><hr size=1> Get a Goranga Idol for Range slot. With a little luck u can get it for free in Maidens, because Idol is LORE and there are sometimes Soloplayer.<br>
<br>
I got mine from a necro, he had 2 rotting there at the same time.<br>
<br>
Hm and I've never heard about a problem with Range and Prim/Sec slot.<br>
<br>
cu <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=229836>Shiaa</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uthorrax.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thorrax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/1/02 5:12:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11682.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hand to Hand weapon help</span><hr size=1> Thank you all very much. <br>
<br>
Seems like all the good Monk gear is on the moon? <br>
<br>
I am still very laggy on the moon even with a new computer (1.3 gig, P4). I hope they work on this because I would like to get some good quality Monk gear on my own instead of paying a fortune for some. But with the weight issues of a Monk, its very hard to even build up a bank account. Took me 40 levels just to get 1800pp. Gezz, my shaman had that at level 20, Lol.<br>
<br>
Thank you all<br>
<br>
Thorrax<br>
Morell-Thule <br>
<br>
