<br>
At 47, your fists are either 13/31 or 13/32 depending on the race and your damage bonus is 7. Even if the fists are 13/31, in your primary hand your fist is only ((13*2)+7)/31 = 106.45<br>
<br>
By way of comparison:<br>
<br>
1. Knuckle Dusters: ((14*2)+7)/28 = 125.00<br>
<br>
2. Fighting Baton: ((8*2)+7)/20 = 115.00<br>
<br>
3. Cane of the Tranquil: ((11*2)+7)/25 = 116.00<br>
<br>
Your fists do get better at higher levels, surpassing Knuckle Dusters at 59/60 depending on the race. But you have to admit that KDs at 59 are not exactly great weapons.<br>
<br>
However, there is yet another problem with using HTH weapons in your high 40s - your HTH is capped at 225 prior to 51, but your 1HB is capped at 240. That's one heck of a difference in your ATK rating. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71792 target=_blank>Scalia</a> /  <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71783 target =_blank>Gluon</a> on E'ci</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=wubao>Wubao</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grand Master</span><br>  Posts: 1543<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/1/02 7:32:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11682.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> says who?</span><hr size=1> &quot;But you have to admit that KDs at 59 are not exactly great weapons.&quot;<br>
<br>
Wow, how mudflated have we become?<br>
<br>
At level 60 your NON-EPIC, naked fists' ratio are almost as good as the RANGER primary hand EPIC sword.<br>
<br>
14/24 on Earthcaller. 14/26 on your fists.<br>
<br>
Yeah, your fists are fine for what they are. A useful, powerful, high damage weapon that COSTS YOU NOTHING and is SOULBOUND.<br>
<br>
Sure, on the moon of Luclin and in a few select spots around the continents of Kunark and Velious you will find weapons that are better than your naked fists, or Knuckledusters.<br>
<br>
But this doesn't make the weapon any less great than it really is.<br>
<br>
It IS a great weapon. There's just been a steady stream of better weapons since that expansion came out.<br>
<br>
/sigh<br>
<br>
-Wu <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugaichin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gaichin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 73<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/2/02 2:28:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11682.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.bestweb.net/~buddha/pstgif.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: says who?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I am still very laggy on the moon even with a new computer (1.3 gig, P4)<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
